1991;;Scenes from a Mall;;American;;Paul Mazursky;;Woody Allen, Bette Midler;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scenes_from_a_Mall;;Nick (Allen), a sports lawyer, is married to psychotherapist and author Deborah (Midler). After years of being happily married, Nick reveals to Deborah that he has had an affair. She is soon shocked and requests a divorce, but later admits that she herself has been unfaithful.